# New Workspace Package

## Checklist

1. Create `packages/<name>/package.json` with scope `{{scope}}`
2. Add `"type-check": "tsc --noEmit"` to scripts
3. Create `packages/<name>/tsconfig.json`
4. Create `packages/<name>/src/index.ts`
5. Run `{{project.packageManager}} install`
6. Update root `AGENTS.md` packages table
